name: Emblemicons
description:
Emblemicons is an open-source free to use library of 1000+ most commonly and frequently used icons. You can use these icons in product development, product design, software development, business presentations, academic projects, to name a few. It is completely free for personal and commercial use.


We are "#4 Product of the Day" on Product Hunt. Come and find us on Product Hunt at - https://www.producthunt.com/posts/emblemicons


You can find us at - https://emblemicons.in

You can read about us in our blog at - https://emblemicons.in/blog
